com.radiantlogic.iddm.schema

Annotation Type Attribute


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value=FIELD)
public @interface Attribute
    Marks a Java field for inclusion as an attribute within a schema object during IDDM schema generation.

    • Optional Element Summary

      Optional Elements 
      Modifier and Type Optional Element and Description
      Field.Type asType
      Specifies the data type used to represent this attribute in the schema.
      boolean isNamingAttribute
      Specifies whether this is a naming attribute used to determine its enclosing schema object's uniqueness.
      boolean isNullable
      Specifies whether the attribute is allowed to have a null value or not.
      String name
      Specifies a custom attribute name.
      String[] tags
      Specifies optional tags that can be applied to the attribute.

    • Element Detail

      • name

        public abstract String name
        Specifies a custom attribute name.

        If provided, this name will be used to create a new attribute in its enclosing schema object. Otherwise, the Java field's name will be used. The name must follow the same rules as a Java identifier: include only ASCII letters, numbers, and underscores and begin with a letter.

        Default:
        ""

      • asType

        public abstract Field.Type asType
        Specifies the data type used to represent this attribute in the schema.

        If provided, this data type will be used when creating a new attribute in the schema. Otherwise, the attribute will be represented as a Field.Type#STRING.

        Default:
        com.radiantlogic.iddm.base.Field.Type.STRING

      • isNullable

        public abstract boolean isNullable
        Specifies whether the attribute is allowed to have a null value or not.

        This effectively determines if an attribute is required or not. All attributes are required by default. This value is used when setting the attribute's nullability in the schema.

        Default:
        false

      • tags

        public abstract String[] tags
        Specifies optional tags that can be applied to the attribute.
        Default:
        {}

      • isNamingAttribute

        public abstract boolean isNamingAttribute
        Specifies whether this is a naming attribute used to determine its enclosing schema object's uniqueness.
        Default:
        false
